{"id": "1413738809526583296", "channel_id": "1402538040253087766", "type": 0, "author_id": "183782216353054720", "author_name": "omnichromia", "author_bot": false, "content": "okay! I read it and I didn't feel like it really cleared up all of the confusing elements, so I thought I'd finish up at least on those, but if I'm gonna touch something at all I may as well be thorough. 😅 \nI'm gonna go through her event story since I haven't done that yet, because I want to get a better idea of who she is, but from what I understand so far I feel like the \"emotion state\" mechanic should be called Moods, no? Mood is a term used often when talking about writing, emotion less so. Plus for kits that complex, less words is better if it gets the point across correctly", "timestamp": "2025-09-06T04:13:18.188000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2025-09-06T04:13:38.689000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": null, "flags": 0}
